<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.2">
<l>pōṉāy māmaruti ṉaṭuvēyeṉpol lāmaṇiyē</l>
<l>tēṉē yiṉṉamutē yeṉṟeṉṟēcila kūṟṟuccollat</l>
<l>tāṉē lemperumāṉavaṉeṉṉā kiyoḻintāṉ</l>
<l>vāṉē mānilamēmaṟṟumuṟṟumeṉ ṉuḷḷaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When saying [and] saying ‘you who went in the middle of the myrobalan trees,</l>
<l>my uncut gem, honey, sweet nectar’, making a few utterances,</l>
<l>if he is himself, my lord, he remains being what?</l>
<l>Sky, great earth and all the others that are in my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
